Name: Corporate Lifestyle Simulator
About the game: An isometric orgy of big smashy pixelart and big smashy chiptunes. Battle your way through corporate architecture and brain dead, buzzword-spewing, middle managers using office supplies as weapons to work through your Jungian shadow issues... Fight back against the forces of tyranny and liberate your fellow coworkers from the oppressive evil that dominates them... Smash ALL THE THINGS!
